1505
01:30:48.921 --> 01:30:50.227
FLANNERY [Narrating]:
<i>She was thinking</i>

1506
01:30:50.401 --> 01:30:52.447
<i>that she would run away
with him.</i>

1507
01:30:52.621 --> 01:30:56.538
<i>And that every night.
he would take the leg off.</i>

1508
01:30:56.712 --> 01:30:58.409
