1545
01:33:19.637 --> 01:33:20.856
And I'll tell you
another thing. Hulga.

1546
01:33:21.030 --> 01:33:22.640
you ain't so smart!

1547
01:33:26.078 --> 01:33:27.645
Come on.

1548
01:33:27.819 --> 01:33:30.909
