ever since I was born.

1549
01:33:32.955 --> 01:33:36.175
FLANNERY [Narrating]:
<i>What's more comic and terrible</i>

1550
01:33:36.349 --> 01:33:40.353
<i>than an angular.</i>

1551
01:33:40.527 --> 01:33:42.225
<i>intellectual woman</i>

1552
01:33:42.399 --> 01:33:45.576
<i>approaching God
