1554
01:34:23.353 --> 01:34:28.010
<i>Dear Flannery.
you must feel better soon.</i>

1555
01:34:30.708 --> 01:34:33.972
<i>I miss you. and I hope
your health is safe.</i>

1556
01:34:36.409 --> 01:34:40.631
<i>I've been reading that Thomas
