1557
01:34:40.805 --> 01:34:43.242
<i>I hope you are too.</i>

1558
01:34:43.416 --> 01:34:45.897
<i>Listen to this.</i>

1559
01:34:46.071 --> 01:34:48.247
<i>"At the center of our being
