1560
01:34:48.421 --> 01:34:50.423
<i>which belongs
entirely to God."</i>

1561
01:34:53.731 --> 01:34:56.778
<i>"It is like a pure diamond...</i>

1562
01:34:56.952 --> 01:34:59.302
<i>blazing with
the invisible light</i>

1563
01:34:59.476 --> 01:35:02.000
<i>of heaven."</i>

1564
01:35:12.010 --> 01:35:14.099
<i>"It is in everybody.</i>

