1568
01:35:21.803 --> 01:35:23.674
<i>that would make
all the darkness</i>

1569
01:35:23.848 --> 01:35:27.112
<i>and cruelty of life vanish.</i>

1570
01:35:27.286 --> 01:35:28.853
<i>Completely."</i>

1571
01:35:37.427 --> 01:35:39.124
<i>"I have no program
